  <description><![CDATA[<p>The BEATUS Wellness &amp; Spa Hotel features one of <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland’s</a> largest and most magnificent hotel parks. Surrounded by hundred-year-old trees and gorgeous rose bushes, you are just steps away from the wonderfully refreshing shores of the lake. The rustle of the wind in the trees overhead will carry your cares away.</p>
<p>At the Hotel, immerse yourself in one of Switzerland’s most significant (2,000 m²) and most diverse wellness oases! Explore the unique outdoor salt-water pool and indoor sports pool. The sauna world features seven different saunas and steam baths, plus a relaxation room with waterbeds and a terrace, the "Café le Palmier" with Vital-Bar, and a fitness studio.</p>
<p>Hotel Beatus will spoil your pallet from dusk to dawn with a ¾ gourmet board. From the substantial breakfast buffet or bathrobe breakfast in the wellness world, to the Vitalità lunch, the "Blechchueche" afternoon cake spread, to gourmet dinner with a choice of menus... there is plenty here to nurture your appetite and your soul.</p>
<p>For those looking to get active. Hotel Belvedere have experienced guest-relations managers that know the Thunersee region and the <a data-udi="umb://document/d1bb27ef1cf04b448d45b9dcbfeb2771" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d1bb27ef1cf04b448d45b9dcbfeb2771}" title="Bernese Oberland">Bernese Oberland</a> like the backs of their hands. From Monday to Friday, they carefully put together a cultural, sports and excursion programme to suit all tastes and levels of ability.</p>
<p><span>Transfer Approx. 2hrs 30mins by rail/boat or Postbus from Zurich airport or</span> 3hrs by r<span>ail/boat or Postbus</span> from Geneva airport. <span>Your journey involves 2 changes of train.</span></p>]]></description>
