  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoying a fabulous location, directly on the lakeside and with a spacious lake-facing garden for relaxing. This deluxe hotel is a great favourite in our programme and is renowned for its excellent standards of service and cuisine. Regular boat services depart from the jetty directly in front of the hotel for a wide choice of day excursions, including the nearby towns of <a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7d838fa65a44467f9a85c30c8d2de877" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d838fa65a44467f9a85c30c8d2de877}" title="Lake Thun">Thun</a> and further afield in the <a data-udi="umb://document/d1bb27ef1cf04b448d45b9dcbfeb2771" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d1bb27ef1cf04b448d45b9dcbfeb2771}" title="Bernese Oberland">Bernese Oberland</a>.</p>]]></listingDescription>
